description: Footage of last year's Red Square military parade play on TV as the pandemic mutes celebrations.
title: Coronavirus: Russia marks WW2 Victory Day with subdued celebrations
title_page: Coronavirus: Russia marks WW2 Victory Day with subdued celebrations - BBC News
maintext: Parts of Russia have been on lockdown since late March but the country now has the fifth-highest rate of infections in the world with almost 200,000 confirmed cases.
